# Dashboard UI - Consolidated Implementation Memory

## System Overview
Build a Next.js 15+ TypeScript dashboard with Tailwind CSS for managing NextMavens Platform. Professional design with Inter font, neutral colors, no emojis/gradients.

## Current Status
PRD created, waiting for execution.

## Technical Approach
- Next.js 15 with App Router and TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS with professional color palette (slate/zinc)
- Supabase Auth for authentication
- Client-side Supabase client with RLS
- Realtime subscriptions for live updates
- Server Actions for mutations

## Related PRDs
- Platform Core (consumes APIs)
- WhatsApp Integration (displays instances)
- API Keys and Authentication (key management UI)

## Stories to Implement
- US-001: User Authentication
- US-002: Dashboard Home
- US-003: Organization Switcher
- US-004: Project List View
- US-005: Create Project Modal
- US-006: Service Redirects
- US-007: API Key Management
- US-008: Real-time Notifications
- US-009: Project Settings Page
- US-010: Team Management Page

